Project Overview

This project is an advanced version of the Student Course Enrollment System built using Java Swing (GUI), Multithreading, and Collections Framework.

It provides an interactive interface for managing students, courses, and enrollments while ensuring smooth performance using background threads.

 Features
GUI-based application using Swing
Add students and courses dynamically
Enroll students into courses
Course capacity management
Responsive UI using multithreading
Efficient data handling using ArrayList and HashMap
